@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vhdfmu(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = 0.40
    v1 = tmp
    tmp = wp.sin(((tmp + 0.32 / v0 + 0.53) / (tmp + 0.86 / tmp + 0.56)))
    v0 = 0.13
    v1 = 0.33
    tmp = v0
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.sin(wp.cos(v2 + 0.98)))
    data[tid] = v0
